WITH deleted AS (
                DELETE FROM gpu_prover_queue_fri
                WHERE
                    instance_status = 'dead'
                    OR (
                        instance_status = 'reserved'
                        AND updated_at < NOW() - $1::INTERVAL
                    )
                RETURNING *
            ),
            inserted_count AS (
                INSERT INTO gpu_prover_queue_fri_archive
                SELECT * FROM deleted
            )
            SELECT COUNT(*) FROM deleted
